    <string name="rules_text">Welcome to <b>Campus Capture</b>, the fun game where you and your section compete against the other sections to see who can occupy the most buildings on campus!\n\n
The rules are simple:\n
&#8226; The map shows you all the zones on campus and who they belong to\n
&#8226; A <b>take-over</b> is the time during which zones can be attacked and defended\n
&#8226; Take-overs span the first 15 minutes of every hour\n
&#8226; During every take-over, go to the zone you wish to attack or defend and press the button\n
&#8226; The section with the most players in the same zone captures it\n
&#8226; Zones award different amounts of points depending on how desirable they are\n
&#8226; Follow the amount of points your section has under the scoreboard tab\n
&#8226; If you need help, invite your friends to join you in your effort under the profile tab\n\n
Have fun and good luck!</string>
